## Refactoring 3D Canvas Editor
- [x] Store improvements: added new state variables `transformMode`, `cameraMode`, `shadingMode`, etc. in `store.ts`.
- [x] Interactive Object Manipulation: Refactored `GenericPart.tsx` to use the new transform and snapping logic.
